name: Bounty
Lore: 'One of the most profitable occupations in the galaxy is hunting down and capturing wanted beings. The more notable the quarry, the more profitable the venture.',
Text: 'Deploy on an opponent''s non-droid character. If subsequently captured by a bounty hunter and then transferred to a prison, retrieve Force equal to character''s forfeit -2 and place Effect in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
